        <item>
            <title>Version 2.0.0</title>
            <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 15:23:19 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>5</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.0.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>Provenance 2.0.0</h2>
                <ul>
                  <li><b>A calmer look</b> — a cleaner surface, a slim top bar, a quiet centered timeline. One Add button records everything; files that arrive wait in the Inbox.</li>
                  <li><b>Feedback, end to end</b> — request a clean reading page from any version; the returned notes log against the exact version that answered them.</li>
                  <li><b>Project Backup, automatic</b> — point at a folder and Provenance mirrors the whole project, verified after each sync.</li>
                </ul>
                <p><a href="https://procestra.app/provenance-releases.html">See everything in 2.0.0</a></p>
            ]]></description>
